          </span>
          <span>
            Designed with
            <a
              href="https://ui.shadcn.com/"
              target="_blank"
              class="underline hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200"
              >ShadCN</a
            >
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
